    "notes": "Round 9 serious late-closure rewrite from C10. Intended proof: keep the north-three and bottle frontier, derive B2 as a guest, use a conditional count that triggers only after B2 is known to explain D2/A3/B3, then use the east-column count to force D4. This intentionally tests whether the late closure is explainable without changing proof/runtime semantics."
